# Design System Rules for Component Creation

## CRITICAL: All new components MUST follow these rules

### Color Palette (STRICT)
- **Backgrounds**: Only use `bg-black`, `bg-black/30`, `bg-black/50`, `bg-black/80`
- **Primary Accent**: Only use `red-500`, `red-600`, `red-400` with opacity variants (`/20`, `/30`, `/50`, `/70`)
- **Text**: `text-white` for primary, `text-zinc-300/400/500/600` for secondary
- **Status Colors**: `green-400/500` (success), `blue-300/400/500` (info), `yellow-400/500` (warning)
- **NEVER** use: gray, slate, neutral, or any colors outside this palette

### Typography (REQUIRED)
- **All headings**: MUST use `font-[family-name:var(--font-orbitron)]`
- **Page titles**: `text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-black`
- **Section headings**: `text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold`
- **Body text**: Default font (no Orbitron)
- **Badges**: Always include `font-[family-name:var(--font-orbitron)]`

### Cards (STANDARD PATTERN)
```tsx
<Card className="bg-black p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8 shadow-2xl border border-red-500/50">
  {/* Content */}
</Card>
```
- Background: `bg-black` or `bg-black/30`
- Border: `border border-red-500/50` or `border-red-500/30`
- Padding: `p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8` (responsive)
- Hover: `hover:border-red-500/70 transition-all`

### Buttons (STANDARD PATTERNS)
```tsx
// Primary
<Button className="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-600 hover:from-red-600 hover:to-red-700">

// Outline
<Button variant="outline" className="border-red-500/50 bg-black/30 text-white hover:bg-black/50 hover:border-red-500/70">
```

### Badges (STANDARD PATTERN)
```tsx
<Badge className="bg-red-500/20 border border-red-500/30 text-red-400 font-[family-name:var(--font-orbitron)] text-xs">
```

### Modals/Dialogs (REQUIRED STRUCTURE)
1. Logo at top: `<Logo variant="compact" showLink={false} className="justify-center mb-1" />`
2. Badge: Gradient badge with action label
3. Title: White, centered, Orbitron font
4. Description: Zinc-500, centered, light weight
5. Content: `space-y-4 mt-4`

### Confirmation Dialogs (REQUIRED PATTERN)
**NEVER use `confirm()` or `alert()` - Always use styled Dialog components**

```tsx
// State
const [showDeleteConfirm, setShowDeleteConfirm] = useState(false);
const [itemToDelete, setItemToDelete] = useState<number | null>(null);

// Handler
const handleDelete = (id: number) => {
  setItemToDelete(id);
  setShowDeleteConfirm(true);
};

const confirmDelete = async () => {
  if (!itemToDelete) return;
  // Delete logic here
  setShowDeleteConfirm(false);
  setItemToDelete(null);
};

// Dialog Component
<Dialog open={showDeleteConfirm} onOpenChange={setShowDeleteConfirm}>
  <DialogContent className="border border-red-500/50 bg-black text-white">
    <DialogHeader>
      <Logo variant="compact" showLink={false} className="justify-center mb-1" />
      <Badge className="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500/30 via-red-600/25 to-red-500/30 border border-red-500/40 text-white backdrop-blur-sm font-[family-name:var(--font-orbitron)] text-xs px-3 py-1 w-fit mx-auto">
        Confirm Deletion
      </Badge>
      <DialogTitle className="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold tracking-tight font-[family-name:var(--font-orbitron)] text-white text-center pt-1">
        Delete Item?
      </DialogTitle>
      <DialogDescription className="text-xs sm:text-sm text-zinc-500 text-center font-light">
        Are you sure you want to delete this item? This action cannot be undone.
      </DialogDescription>
    </DialogHeader>
    <div className="mt-4 p-3 rounded-lg border border-red-500/50 bg-black/30">
      <div className="flex items-start gap-2">
        <AlertTriangle className="size-4 text-red-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" />
        <div className="flex-1">
          <p className="text-xs text-red-400 font-[family-name:var(--font-orbitron)] font-semibold mb-1">
            Warning
          </p>
          <p className="text-xs text-zinc-400 font-light">
            Warning message describing the consequences.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div className="flex gap-2 sm:gap-3 pt-3">
      <Button
        type="button"
        variant="outline"
        onClick={() => {
          setShowDeleteConfirm(false);
          setItemToDelete(null);
        }}
        className="flex-1 border-red-500/50 bg-black/30 text-white hover:bg-black/50 hover:border-red-500/70"
      >
        Cancel
      </Button>
      <Button
        type="button"
        onClick={confirmDelete}
        className="flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-red-600 hover:from-red-600 hover:to-red-700"
      >
        Delete
      </Button>
    </div>
  </DialogContent>
</Dialog>
```

**Required Elements:**
- Logo at top
- Gradient badge with action label (e.g., "Confirm Deletion", "Confirm Cancellation")
- Title with Orbitron font, white, centered
- Description with zinc-500 text, centered, light weight
- Warning section with AlertTriangle icon (`text-red-400`)
- Two buttons: Cancel (outline) and Action (gradient red)
- Import `AlertTriangle` from `lucide-react`

### Spacing (CONSISTENT)
- Between sections: `space-y-6`
- Card padding: `p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8`
- Main cards: MUST include `border border-red-500/50`
- Gaps: `gap-3` or `gap-4` (never `gap-1`)
- Button groups: `gap-2 sm:gap-3` with `pt-4` (not `pt-3`)
- Form fields: `space-y-2` (not `space-y-1.5`)
- Card content: `mb-4` for main content, `mb-2` for secondary text
- Button spacing: Always `gap-2` minimum between buttons
- Text spacing: Add `mt-2` to date/secondary text after main content

### Icons
- Sizes: `size-4` (small), `size-5` (medium), `size-8` (large), `size-12` (xlarge)
- Colors: `text-red-400` (primary), `text-zinc-400/500` (secondary)
- With text: `mr-2` or `ml-2`

### Interactive States (REQUIRED)
- Hover: Always include `hover:` variants with `transition-all`
- Active: `active:scale-95` for buttons
- Disabled: `disabled:opacity-50`
- Focus: `focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-red-500/50`

## Checklist Before Committing
- [ ] All headings use Orbitron font
- [ ] Only black/red/zinc/green/blue/yellow colors used
- [ ] Cards have red borders with opacity (`border border-red-500/50`)
- [ ] Buttons follow gradient or outline patterns
- [ ] Badges use opacity backgrounds and `text-xs` size
- [ ] Responsive padding applied (`p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8`)
- [ ] Button spacing: `gap-2` minimum (never `gap-1`)
- [ ] Form spacing: `space-y-2` (not `space-y-1.5`)
- [ ] Button groups: `pt-4` (not `pt-3`)
- [ ] Card content: `mb-4` for main, `mb-2` for secondary
- [ ] Hover states included
- [ ] Icons properly sized and colored
- [ ] Modals include Logo + Badge + Title + Description structure
- [ ] **NO `confirm()` or `alert()` calls - all use styled Dialog components**
- [ ] Confirmation dialogs include Logo + Badge + Title + Description + Warning section
- [ ] Buttons with icons include text labels (not icon-only unless necessary)
- [ ] Cards use `min-w-0` and `flex-shrink-0` appropriately for text wrapping

